    </indexterm>

    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introdução a Unicode::LineBreak</title>

      <para>
        Unicode::LineBreak provides a UAX #14 Unicode Line Breaking Algorithm.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

